  "description": "This individual is a middle-aged human of light skinTone, marked by a square jaw and a prominent, repeatedly broken nose set from years of close-quarters brawls. Brown eyes sit deep beneath heavy brows, giving the face a watchful, assessing cast that never fully relaxes. Black hair is kept in a plain style with a high, practical trim that exposes a furrowed forehead and old crow’s-feet. Thick hands with permanent callus ridges and faint burn-speckling at the knuckles attest to long service behind a bar and frequent work with hot glass and harsh spirits.",
